        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nDear Ganesh,\n\nThank your for contributing. Regarding to Saltstack adapter, since we passed M1 planning for R3 already, Saltstack is not in the scope for R3. I would suggest you leave your change as a draft until we branch out R3. The possible date to branch would be mid of September. but let me know your thoughts. -Taka",
